import React from 'react' import PaymentModel from '../../../Models/PaymentModel' const PaymentListCard:React.FC<{payments:PaymentModel[] | undefined}> = () => { return ( <> {messages.map((message: MessageModel, index: number) => (
{message.messageSenderName}
{message.messageTitle}

{message.messageBody.length > 50 ? `${message.messageBody.slice(0,50)}...` : message.messageBody}

{message.createdAt.slice(0,16)}

))} ) } export default PaymentListCard
